### 루틴 목록 조회
GET {{memory_api}}/api/v1/routines
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 루틴 미리보기 조회
GET {{memory_api}}/api/v1/routines/preview?startDate=2025-07-22&endDate=2025-07-28
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 루틴 수정
PUT {{memory_api}}/api/v1/routines/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "title": "매일 물 마시기 (수정)",
  "content": "하루에 물 10잔 마시기",
  "repeatType": "DAILY",
  "interval": 1,
  "startDate": "2025-07-22",
  "endDate": null
}

### 루틴 활성화/비활성화
PATCH {{memory_api}}/api/v1/routines/1/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 루틴 삭제
DELETE {{memory_api}}/api/v1/routines/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Todo와 루틴 미리보기 함께 조회
GET {{memory_api}}/api/v1/todos/combined?startDate=2025-07-22&endDate=2025-07-28
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 루틴을 Todo로 변환
POST {{memory_api}}/api/v1/todos/convert-routine
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "routineId": 1,
